(443, 149, 119, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Tecco Garden apartment complex has won the hearts of residents for what reasons?', 'Tecco Garden apartment complex has won over residents by establishing stable operations and creating a civilized community. It has achieved this through its existing values such as green spaces, comprehensive amenities, and spacious apartments', '<p>Tecco Garden apartment complex has won over residents by establishing stable operations and creating a civilized community. It has achieved this through its existing values such as green spaces, comprehensive amenities, and spacious apartments</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>A fulfilling life comes from practical values.</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Anyone passing by the Tứ Hiệp urban area (Thanh Tr&igrave;) will be drawn to the apartment complex consisting of four prominent white high-rise buildings named Tecco Garden. True to its name, Tecco Garden is surrounded by lush greenery in the park and internal roads.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Adjacent to the project is the Thanh Tr&igrave; planned park, offering easy visibility of the Hồng River, Y&ecirc;n Sở Park, and Linh Đ&agrave;m Lake from the apartment windows. To date, 3/4 of the apartments at Tecco Garden have welcomed residents, creating a vibrant and lively residential community.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the morning, the elderly go down to the communal park to exercise, play chess, and have conversations. In the afternoon, groups of children play and frolic in the playground, while parents work out in the on-site gym and yoga rooms. In the evening, the whole family goes to the supermarket together, strolls along the internal roads.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mr. L&ecirc; Hải, a resident of the project, shared that ever since they sold their house in Ho&agrave;ng Mai and moved into a 3-bedroom +1 apartment at Tecco Garden, the whole family, including grandparents, parents, and children, feels happier.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;My wife and I may need an extra 7 minutes to commute to work, but in return, we have a more spacious apartment and a greener environment, making every moment at home complete and serene. What&#39;s more important is that our grandparents have space to relax, and our children can play and develop comprehensively.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ms. Nguyễn Thị Quỳnh Thơ, the owner of the largest apartment in the project with an area of 141m2, shared her reason for &quot;leaving the city&quot; and moving to Tecco Garden: &quot;The top criterion that I value more in Tecco Garden compared to other projects is the living space and size.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Living space is priceless, something that money can&#39;t buy. As for size, instead of living in a cramped small house in the city center, I chose a 4-bedroom apartment here to optimize functionality and provide individual space for each family member,&quot; added Ms. Quỳnh Thơ.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It can be said that Tecco Garden has become an ideal residence for hundreds of families, where the apartment is a spacious home for the entire family, surrounded by fresh green spaces and modern amenities right at their doorstep.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Introducing the &quot;sky villa&quot; model of 141m2</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Not only satisfying the residents who have already moved in, Tecco Garden continues to attract interested customers by preparing to launch a model apartment with a spacious area of 141m2, the largest in the project.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"Căn mẫu &quot;biệt thự trên không&quot; tại Tecco Garden được thiết kế theo phong cách tân cổ điển kết hợp hiện đại\" src=\"https://datxanhindochine.com/public/uploads/tin-tuc/photo-1-16875722088271202787652-1687580962040-16875809621831093215079.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">The &#39;sky villa&#39; model at Tecco Garden is designed in a modern-classic style fusion</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the vision of transforming Tecco Garden apartments into &quot;sky garden villas,&quot; Dat Xanh Northern Region has raised the standard of handover equipment from mid-range to high-end.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Specifically, in addition to the built-in wall furniture in the existing finishing list provided by the Tecco Group, Dat Xanh Northern Region has upgraded and supplemented the handover standards to include ceilings, walls, floors, smart home devices, water heaters, sanitary equipment, and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The apartment consists of 3 bedrooms and 1 multipurpose room, with all 3 main bedrooms having spacious sizes ranging from 12.5 to 20.8m2 and large windows that allow natural light to enter. The master bedroom, with a size of 20.8m2, has its own loggia and is spacious enough to accommodate a dressing room or workspace.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The multipurpose room has a size of up to 10m2, equivalent to the main bedroom in many other projects, making it versatile for use as a maid&#39;s room, prayer room, reading room, or gym.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The main loggia is a generous 8.1m2, located between the living room and kitchen, providing both light and serving activities such as laundry and cooking. The kitchen area is specially designed to be completely separate from the common area and can accommodate an island counter to enhance the aesthetic appeal of the home while avoiding cooking odors</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"Logia căn hộ được thiết kế thành không gian thư giãn đầy thi vị cho gia chủ\" src=\"https://datxanhindochine.com/public/uploads/tin-tuc/photo-2-1687572208331541754561-1687580963350-1687580963443806674617.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><em>The loggia of the apartment is designed as a delightful and relaxing space for the homeowners.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The loggia of the apartment is thoughtfully designed to create a serene and enjoyable space for the homeowners. It serves as a perfect retreat where they can unwind, relax, and indulge in their favorite activities. The carefully selected furniture and decor elements add to the ambiance, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether it&#39;s a cozy reading nook, a mini garden with potted plants, or a comfortable seating area to enjoy a cup of coffee, the loggia offers a versatile space for the homeowners to personalize according to their preferences. It provides a seamless transition between the indoor and outdoor areas, allowing residents to connect with nature while enjoying the comfort of their home.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The loggia at Tecco Garden apartments is truly a haven of relaxation and enjoyment, providing a private retreat where the homeowners can escape from the hustle and bustle of daily life and find tranquility in their own sanctuary.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'en', NULL, NULL, '2023-06-27 04:19:32', '2023-06-27 04:19:32');
